    "description": "<p>At CHAGEE, we are Passionate Purveyors of TEA, and it is the very</p>\n<p>heart and soul of our business. Our journey is fueled by a deep-rooted</p>\n<p>commitment to sourcing, crafting, and sharing the finest teas from</p>\n<p>around the world. With a relentless pursuit of quality, innovation, and</p>\n<p>sustainability, we have emerged as industry leaders, redefining the</p>\n<p>tea experience from November 17, 2017, with the first store in Yunnan</p>\n<p>China.</p>\n<p>Now we’ve grown to more than 29 provinces and cities in mainland</p>\n<p>China, and has also opened stores in Southeast Asia like Malaysia,</p>\n<p>Singapore, and Thailand. As of 2024, we have over 5,000+ stores globally.</p>",
